Author: Ben Frederickson <github@benfrederickson.com>
Date:   Thu Oct 8 21:06:13 2015 -0700

    Fix issues with completely overlapped circles

     * sortAreas wasn't setting Z-order appropiately (#49)
     * computeTextCentres was occasionally returning incorrect output (#48)

    Both of these should be fixed here, by figuring out all overlapping circles
    and taking into account. Also there is a better fall back in
    computeTextCentres (trying again without exterior circles).
