Author: Ben Frederickson <github@benfrederickson.com>
Date:   Tue May 12 23:24:27 2015 -0700

    better algorithm for computing text centres

    There were a couple issues with the previous method for calculating label
    positions, https://github.com/benfred/venn.js/issues/25#issuecomment-78005285
    and https://github.com/benfred/venn.js/issues/18#issuecomment-53161777 show
    some of the issues.

    Fix this by computing the point where the margin (distance to other circles)
    is maximized for each intersection area.
